All Classes

  • All Classes Class Summary Enum Summary 
    Class Description
    Game
    This Game class initializes the game, manages the user status, and creates the Win scenarios for the game.
    House
    This class acts as a model for a house in the game that users can visit and interact with.
    Main  
    Neighborhood
    This class acts as a model for the neighborhood that a user will be playing in throughout a game.
    Player
    This class acts as a model for the Player's character throughout a game.
    PlayMusic
    This class is responsible for all background-music-related audio, including the playing, stopping, and changing the volume of background music.
    SoundEffects
    This class is responsible for all sound-effect-related audio, including the playing, stopping, and changing the volume of sound effects.
    State
    This class acts as a model for the current state of a game (a game can be either won, lost, or still playing).
    StoreGame
    This class is responsible for saving the current game data and loading previously saved game data.
    TextParser
    This class is responsible for parsing a user input and checking whether the input is a valid game command.
    View
    Represents the data to be displayed to the user in a game.
